issue.title: How to replay logs from cloudsim?

content.raw:
yeah the model has recently been updated. You can download version 3 of the subt tunnel staging area like so:

`ign fuel download --url "https://fuel.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/models/subt_tunnel_staging_area/3" -v 4`

I noticed that it prints out a warning msg but still downloads the model successfully
